orange-pl (1:0.3) unstable; urgency=low

  * Completely new configuration file
  * Drop phonebook support (use external programs instead: 'Person2Number',
    'Number2Person' configuration options)
  * Drop '--debug' option (use 'Debug' configuration option instead)
  * Actions '-s' and '-S' does not differ any more (use 'RejectUnpersons'
    configuration option or '--force' option instead)
  * Change file names:
    - 'orange-pl-cookie-jar.txt' -> 'cookie-jar.txt'

 -- Jakub Wilk <ubanus@users.sf.net>  Thu, 27 Jul 2006 12:03:28 +0200

